@startuml
' C4-style decomposition (lightweight): Context + container + interfaces
left to right direction

!define PERSON(name,descr) actor "name\ndescr" as name
!define SYSTEM(name,descr) rectangle "name\ndescr" as name
!define CONTAINER(name,descr) rectangle "name\ndescr" as name
!define QUEUE(name,descr) database "name\ndescr" as name

title zkSEC C4-style Architecture

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 5
}

PERSON(Operator, "Human operator")
PERSON(Maintainer, "Maintainer/authorized actor")

SYSTEM(zkSEC, "zkSEC policy surface\n(offline decision gateway)")
SYSTEM(AdjacentSystems, "Adjacent systems\n(kant-zk-pastebin, zos-server)")
SYSTEM(Zkperf, "zkperf witness tooling")

CONTAINER(DecisionEngine, "Security policy engine\n\u2022 assess_action\n\u2022 assess_data_boundary")
CONTAINER(Contracts, "Adapter contracts\n\u2022 action allowlists\n\u2022 resource roots")
CONTAINER(Geometry, "Capability geometry\n\u2022 action capability profiles\n\u2022 channel/ring/destination checks")
CONTAINER(Admissibility, "Transform admissibility\n\u2022 proposal-only ZOS bridge\n\u2022 unified detector\n\u2022 ontology checks\n\u2022 attack harness")
CONTAINER(Routing, "Routing and receipts\n\u2022 evaluate_adapter_action\n\u2022 policy receipts")
CONTAINER(Execution, "Execution gate\n\u2022 build_execution_directive")
CONTAINER(Reporting, "Reporting\n\u2022 execution_audit_record")

QUEUE(AuditStore, "Evidence store\nchangelog, milestones, tests, traces")

Operator --> zkSEC : CLI request\n(action, resource, payload)
Maintainer --> zkSEC : authorization\n(actor_identity, plan_ref, scope)

zkSEC --> DecisionEngine : evaluate action contract
zkSEC --> Contracts : resolve adapter profile
Contracts --> Geometry : supplies action geometry
zkSEC --> Admissibility : evaluate transform tuple
zkSEC --> Routing : compose gate + adapter decisions
Routing --> Execution : produce execution directive
Execution --> Reporting : command + reason code
Reporting --> AuditStore : deterministic audit records

DecisionEngine --> AuditStore : policy receipts\n(boundary/allow/deny)
Admissibility --> AuditStore : admissibility verdicts\nbridge/detector metadata
Contracts --> AdjacentSystems : declared action contracts
zkSEC --> Zkperf : no live outbound calls\n(reference-only witness traces)

note right of DecisionEngine
  Invariant: resource scope normalized\nand URI-like paths rejected
end note

note right of Geometry
  Invariant: geometry requests must stay\ninside action and adapter envelope
end note

note right of Admissibility
  Invariant: proposal metadata never becomes authority\nwithout explicit managed promotion
end note

note right of Execution
  Invariant: high-authority actions\nrequire identity + scope + plan_ref
end note

note right of zkSEC
  No outbound network/process execution\nin this local surface.
end note

@enduml
